{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-program-year-js","path":"/programs/open-hardware-creators-in-academia/2022-2023/","result":{"data":{"contentfulProgramYear":{"id":"8d993a17-564f-54fb-8052-6967976a1fdd","title":"2022-2023","program":[{"id":"3a0eb8d1-0cd4-505d-a937-b61e4534ee13","title":"OHCA Fellows","prettyUrl":"open-hardware-creators-in-acadamia-fellows"}],"shortDescription":{"childrenMarkdownRemark":[{"html":"<p>Our 2024 Open Hardware Creators in Academia Fellows was made possible by the Sloan Foundation, and ran from 2022-2023 in its inaugural year. This Fellowship focused on educators telling other educators how to build, use and procure more open source hardware in their universities and institutions, which culminated in a series of documentation, including an Enabling Practices written for higher education.</p>"}]},"headerImage":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/3e0cshhzqlmj/52Eydrl4vY1dld5NrMOAo6/a811ab3572199c25b31312f2130f1fc5/lab-halftone.png"},"fellows":[{"id":"413647fd-f34b-54fb-b645-3ad2086c9b9e","displayName":"Dr. AnnMarie Thomas","prettyUrl":"annmarie-thomas","title":"Professor","affiliation":"University of St. Thomas","image":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/3e0cshhzqlmj/4psVwl38uTiJ6A55gcwOA5/8e27930b053cff7860c5c1a88471ebf7/AmptYellowLights-AnnMarie-Thomas.png"}},{"id":"70b6d71e-5475-5957-8fe1-181fb371831d","displayName":"Dr. Carlotta Berry","prettyUrl":"carlotta-berry","title":"Professor","affiliation":"Rose-Hulman Institute of Technology","image":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/3e0cshhzqlmj/5xGfZ2yCrfYNqdVstK3utx/10242f3b4ac9e4081d1280d614cdeedc/Berry_-Carlotta_2016-Carlotta-A.-Berry-PhD1.png"}},{"id":"1eb0f9c5-6ae6-5502-9fd4-64a880627ebe","displayName":"Dahl Winters","prettyUrl":"dahl-winters","title":"Ph.D Candidate","affiliation":"Colorado State University","image":{"url":"https://images.ctfassets.net/3e0cshhzqlmj/316XNuY2a7mCUK6CebHVPE/d3cf7f3718701088b01b291c7144d071/dw_headshot_ebc-Dahl-Winters.png"}},{"id":"ce6d